Start Node server with
----------------------
yarn run dev

Add to package.json
-------------------
"scripts": {
  "dev": "./node_modules/nodemon/bin/nodemon.js app.js"
}

Dependacies
-----------
yarn add nodemon dotenv express mongoose

Configure /etc/mongod.conf 
----------------------------
change default bingIp: 127.0.0.1 to 0.0.0.0